## рҹҡЁ Emergency Alert Types

| Alert | Icon | Use Case |
|---|---|---|
| **FIRE** | рҹ”Ҙ | Active fire, smoke hazard, building evacuation |
| **MEDICAL** | рҹҡ‘ | Medical emergency, injury, need for first aid or ambulance |
| **EVACUATION** | вҡ пёҸ | Ordered evacuation of an area, dangerous zone |
| **SOS** | рҹҶҳ | General distress signal вҖ” life-threatening, need immediate help |

Each alert is tagged with the sender's live GPS coordinates at the time of broadcast, allowing recipients to know the geographic origin of the emergency.

